Gumawa ka ng modern and clean authentication page design gamit ang TailwindCSS. Kailangan ko ng login at registration form sa isang page na may tab switching.

DESIGN REQUIREMENTS:

1. COLOR SCHEME:
   - Main background: Slate-50 (bg-slate-50)
   - Card background: White
   - Primary color: Indigo-600 (buttons, active tab)
   - Text colors: Slate-900 para sa headings, Slate-500 para sa subtext
   - Border colors: Slate-100 or Slate-200

2. CARD/LAYOUT:
   - Centered sa screen gamit ang flex
   - White card na may rounded-3xl (border-radius: 24px)
   - May subtle shadow: shadow-2xl shadow-indigo-100
   - May border: border border-slate-100
   - Maximum width: max-w-md (28rem / 448px)
   - Padding: p-8 (2rem)

3. HEADER SECTION:
   - Title: "Welcome Back" (text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900)
   - Subtitle: "Enter your details to access your account" (text-slate-500 text-sm)

4. TAB SWITCHING:
   - Grid na may 2 columns (Sign In at Register)
   - Background: bg-slate-100 na may rounded-2xl
   - Active tab: White background, shadow-sm, text-indigo-600
   - Inactive tab: text-slate-500, hover:text-slate-700
   - Transition: smooth transition-all

5. FORM FIELDS:
   - Labels: text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400
   - Inputs: w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl
   - Focus effect: ring-2 ring-indigo-500/20 focus:border-indigo-500
   - Transition: transition-all outline-none

6. LOGIN FORM:
   - Email field
   - Password field na may "Forgot password?" link
   - Submit button: w-full py-3.5 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-xl font-bold
   - Hover effect: bg-indigo-700
   - Active effect: scale-[0.98]

7. REGISTER FORM:
   - Full Name, Email, Password, Confirm Password fields
   - Terms and Conditions checkbox na naka-disable at hindi clickable hangga't hindi nababasa ang terms
   - Terms link na nag-o-open ng modal
   - Submit button

8. TERMS CHECKBOX (IMPORTANT LOGIC):
   - Initially disabled at may opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed
   - May modal na nagpapakita ng Terms and Conditions
   - Dapat mag-scroll ang user hanggang dulo ng terms bago ma-enable ang "I have read" button
   - Kapag na-click ang "I have read" button:
     * Maa-enable ang checkbox
     * Auto-check ang checkbox
     * Hindi na maaaring i-uncheck ng user
     * Magsasara ang modal
   - Kapag nag-submit ang form, i-validate na checked ang checkbox

9. TERMS MODAL:
   - Fixed overlay: bg-slate-900/50
   - White card: rounded-3xl p-8 max-w-lg
   - Terms content: h-64 overflow-y-auto
   - Accept button: disabled hangga't hindi na-scroll sa dulo
   - Scroll detection: kapag scrolled to bottom, mag-e-enable ang button

10. DIVIDER:
    - "Or continue with" na may border lines sa magkabilang gilid
    - Relative positioning na may absolute border

11. GOOGLE BUTTON:
    - White background na may border
    - Hover: bg-slate-50
    - May Google SVG icon
    - Text: "Sign in with Google"

12. ERROR/STATUS MESSAGES:
    - Error: red-600 bg-red-50 rounded-xl
    - Success: emerald-600 bg-emerald-50 rounded-xl
    - Auto-hide after 5 seconds

13. RESPONSIVE:
    - Mobile-friendly
    - Minimum padding: p-4 sa body
    - Full width sa mobile, centered sa desktop

14. ANIMATIONS:
    - Button hover effects
    - Active scale effect
    - Smooth transitions
    - Flash message fade out

Ito ay login/registration page para sa Laravel application. Gumamit ng Laravel Blade syntax para sa forms at routes ({{ route('server.login') }}, @csrf, etc.). Dapat may JavaScript functions para sa tab switching, terms modal, at scroll detection.

Gawin mong professional, modern, at user-friendly ang design. Ang checkbox ay dapat LOCKED hangga't hindi nababasa ang terms sa modal.